{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Spell Spiral</strong> is a fast-paced action shooting game where players battle using spells, decks, mana, etc., just like in a card game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Basic boss battles only. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Conquer powerful enemies through repeated trial and error.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About the trial version</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The trial version only allows you to play two stages of normal mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Also, the trial version has fewer spells available than the main game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Player controls like a card game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296890/extras/HeavyLaser.jpg?t=1730277583\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The most distinctive feature of this game is the player's control method. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are no normal attacks, and you use the spell that is set at that time with the ABXY button. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are various types of spells, including simple shooting, homing bullets, self-strengthening, and healing. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Also, using spells consumes mana. Of course, the more powerful the spell, the more mana it will consume. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The total number of decks is 20, and if the deck runs out of spells during battle, the powerful spell &quot;Highlander Spell&quot; can be used, and then a new deck will be replenished and shuffled. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Beautiful and brutal barrage of bullets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296890/extras/BulletHell1.jpg?t=1730277583\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each enemy launches a barrage of bullets that is incredibly intense. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customize your deck to your liking</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296890/extras/DeckEdit.jpg?t=1730277583\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Before battle, you can edit the contents of the deck you will use. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make a deck with a concept in mind, such as more shooting or more lasers. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Include many effective spells to match the enemy. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Include many healing spells because you are not confident in avoiding attacks. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your deck with various ideas in mind.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296890/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730277583","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296890/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1730277583","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296890/5d0b7a39be3225454eac76fd44947908ce37cb80/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730277583","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296890/5d0b7a39be3225454eac76fd44947908ce37cb80/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730277583","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p c